      "y": 125,
      "width": 242,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "All invest for SAME duration\nProfit ratio = Capital ratio\n\nA:B = Cₐ : Cᵦ\nA's share = Profit × Cₐ/(Cₐ+Cᵦ)",
