    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 278,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 94,
      "text": "Split into periods at each change\nEffective capital = Σ(Cᵢ × Tᵢ)\n\nA invests C₁ for t₁, then C₂ for t₂\nA's effective = C₁×t₁ + C₂×t₂\nCompare effective capitals for ratio",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
