    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 548,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A = 4000x12 = 48000\n        B = 6000x8 = 48000\nStep 2: Ratio = 48000:48000 = 1:1\nStep 3: Each = 2400/2 = Rs 1200\n\nTRICK:\nCapital x Time ratio decides split\n4000x12 = 6000x8 (equal!)\nSo equal split: 1200 each\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 1200, B = Rs 1200 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
