    {
      "id": "el_30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 548,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A:B = 20000:25000 = 4:5\nStep 2: Total = 9 parts\nStep 3: B = 9000 x 5/9 = Rs 5000\n\nTRICK:\n1 part = 9000/9 = 1000\nB = 5 x 1000 = Rs 5000\nA = 4 x 1000 = Rs 4000\n\nAnswer: B's share = Rs 5000 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
