    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 903,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A salary = 100x12 = Rs 1200/yr\nStep 2: Remaining = 2000-1200 = 800\n  Capital 1:1 → each gets 400\nStep 3: A=1200+400=1600, B=400\n\nTRICK:\nDeduct salary first, split rest by ratio\n  Profit ═══ 2000\n  ├─ Salary ── 1200 (A only)\n  └─ Rest ──── 800 → 1:1 split\n  A=1600, B=400\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 1600, B = Rs 400 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4000,
