      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A salary = 100x12 = Rs 1200/yr\nStep 2: Remaining = 2000-1200 = 800\n  Capital 1:1 → each gets 400\nStep 3: A=1200+400=1600, B=400\n\nTRICK:\nDeduct salary first, split rest by ratio\n  Profit ═══ 2000\n  ├─ Salary ── 1200 (A only)\n  └─ Rest ──── 800 → 1:1 split\n  A=1600, B=400\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 1600, B = Rs 400 ✓",
