      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=12mo, B=12-4=8mo\nStep 2: A=8000x12=96k, B=12000x8=96k\nStep 3: Ratio=1:1, each=5400/2=2700\n\n  Month: 1────4──────────12\n  A:     |════════════════| 8kx12\n  B:         |════════════| 12kx8\n\nTRICK:\nCxT products equal → equal split\n8000x12 = 12000x8 = 96000\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 2700, B = Rs 2700 ✓",
