    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1271,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=6000x8=48k, B=8000x12=96k\nStep 2: Ratio = 48:96 = 1:2\nStep 3: A=2380x1/3=793, B=2380x2/3=1587\n\n  Month: 1──────8──────────12\n  A:     |═══════| 6kx8=48k\n  B:     |════════════════| 8kx12=96k\n\nTRICK:\nCxT ratio = 48:96 = 1:2\n1 part = 2380/3 = 793.33\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 793, B = Rs 1587 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
