      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=6000x8=48k, B=8000x12=96k\nStep 2: Ratio = 48:96 = 1:2\nStep 3: A=2380x1/3=793, B=2380x2/3=1587\n\n  Month: 1──────8──────────12\n  A:     |═══════| 6kx8=48k\n  B:     |════════════════| 8kx12=96k\n\nTRICK:\nCxT ratio = 48:96 = 1:2\n1 part = 2380/3 = 793.33\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 793, B = Rs 1587 ✓",
