    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1287,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A = 10kx6 + 15kx6 = 150k\n        B = 15kx12 = 180k\nStep 2: Ratio = 150:180 = 5:6\nStep 3: A=3500x5/11=1591, B=1909\n\n  Month: 1────6──────────12\n  A:     |=10k=|===15k====|\n  B:     |======15k=======|\n\nTRICK:\nSplit periods at capital change\nEffective = sum(Capital x Time)\nRatio 5:6 → 1 part = 3500/11\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 1591, B = Rs 1909 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
