      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A profit=600, B profit=900\nStep 2: Ratio = 600:900 = 2:3\nStep 3: Same time → capital = 2:3\n  6000/B = 2/3 → B = 9000\n\nTRICK:\nB/A profit = 900/600 = 3/2\nB capital = A capital x 3/2\n= 6000 x 3/2 = Rs 9000\n\nAnswer: B invested Rs 9000 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
