    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1700,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A = 500x(12+11+...+1)\n  = 500x78 = 39000\nStep 2: B = 3000x12 = 36000\nStep 3: Ratio = 39:36 = 13:12\n  A=1200x13/25=624, B=576\n\nTRICK:\nMonthly invest: sum = nx(n+1)/2\nA = 500 x 12x13/2 = 39000\nRatio 13:12, 1 part = 1200/25 = 48\n\nAnswer: A = Rs 624, B = Rs 576 ✓",
